comments: Kuzma (WAS) is retreating alongside Aldridge's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact in the post.
Harrell (WAS) briefly grasps Edwards' (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs as Harrell firms up during the pick.
Beal (WAS) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes more than two steps after his gather.
Edwards (BKN) is retreating alongside Beal's (WAS) path and maintains verticality as he defends the shot near the rim.
Beal (WAS) briefly grasps Aldridge's (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs as they disengage following the pick.
Kuzma (WAS) legally contests Aldridge's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Edwards (BKN) moves forward into Beal's (WAS) path and initiates contact that affects his FOM off ball.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) extends his hand forward into Irving's (BKN) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Harrell (WAS) wraps Aldridge (BKN) prior to making any contact with the ball.
Harrell (WAS) is already in Irving's (BKN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Irving (BKN) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Beal (WAS) in the backcourt.
Aldridge (BKN) is already in Dinwiddie's (WAS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Aldridge (BKN) is already in Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Harrell (WAS) and Aldridge (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Harrell (WAS) brings his hand forward towards Harden's (BKN) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Mills (BKN) applies his hand momentarily to Harrell's (WAS) side and immediately removes his hand as they pursue the rebound.  The two then briefly engage and disengage.
As Harrell (WAS) is falling out of bounds, he attempts to call a timeout, which is not recognized by the crew.
Harden (BKN) legally contests Dinwiddie's (WAS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
